  "text": "The MOLES developed by [CITATION_1] that comprised of 35 items scale and six subscales: metacognitive demands, within-class discourse, teacher encouragement and support, distributed control, emotional support, and student voice. The reliability of the measure examined by internal consistency Chronbach alpha method. Alpha coefficient toward metacognitive demands, within-class discourse, teacher encouragement and support, distributed control, emotional support, and student voice was 0.84, 0.91, 0.76, 0.82 and 0.65 respectively. The validity of the measure examined to factor analysis method.",
